data.value: This launcher simplify some things for average user. Launcher... 1. Fixes long loading problem of the game. 2. Fixes problems, that may appear in system registry. 3. Allows easy install 4GB patch. 4. Has buttons that make easy to open Mods and Maps folders for new user. 5. Has built-in mods launch withoit additional command-line arguments such as "-ui"
